  "texts": [
    "Deep Learning (DL) is a type of ML.",
    "While DL does not always require clear instructions, can improve through human feedback.",
    "This approach is known as Reinforcement Learning from Human Feedback (RLHF).",
    "The emergence of chatbots and similar tools has been enabled by models trained on sequential data in lieu of individual data items (phrases and entire sentences in lieu of words), allowing them to process and generate long streams of information.",
    "These \"transformer\" models represent phrases and sentences as numerical arrays."
  ],
